<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc00d20ff-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s16314"><num value="16314">§ 16314.</num><heading> Hydrogen</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idc00d2100-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s16314/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> In general</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall conduct a program of fundamental research and development in support of programs authorized under subchapter VIII.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idc00d2101-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s16314/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Methods</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The program shall include support for methods of generating hydrogen without the use of natural gas.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idc00d2102-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/58/tIX/s974">Pub. L. 109–58, title IX, § 974</ref>, <date date="2005-08-08">Aug. 8, 2005</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/119/903">119 Stat. 903</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
